  description: 'This is a prefab, which means you can pull it into your scene and
    override specific settings like materials or textures to fit your needs.



    The
    best part is that these changes only stay on the object in the scene. You can
    still drag the original version from your project window to get a fresh, default
    copy whenever you want. This is especially helpful for things like these picture
    frames, as it lets you use the same base model throughout your world while giving
    each one a unique image.'
